  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2cbaeec8dbe84e069925173ac3a6210b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dlg_Forest_GM_Opening
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ElementalAlchemist.Dialogue.DialogueData
  _speaker: Grand Master
  _lines:
  - This forest breathes with elements waiting to be gathered.
  - Collect what you find, carry it back to the village, and fuse it. Always try new pairings; that is how mastery is built.
  - But gathering alone will never make you great. Deep in these woods lives the Guardian of the Forest.
  - Seek it out and prove yourself. It keeps a Fragment that will make you stronger than any common alchemist, and I mean for you to have it.
